@startuml Seq-02 Reserve a Spot

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 5
skinparam sequenceParticipant underline

actor       "Driver"            as Driver
participant "API Gateway"       as GW
participant "Reservation Svc"   as Reservation
participant "Payment Service"   as Payment
participant "Payment Gateway"   as PGW
database    "PostgreSQL"        as DB
database    "Redis"             as Redis

== Common: Idempotency & Validation ==

Driver -> GW : POST /reservations\n{ idempotency_key, vehicle_type, mode, [spot_id] }
GW -> Reservation : CreateReservation(request)

Reservation -> DB : SELECT r.*, r.qr_code_url, s.spot_code, s.floor_number\nFROM reservations r JOIN spots s ON s.id = r.spot_id\nWHERE r.idempotency_key=$1

alt idempotency_key already exists (duplicate request)
    DB --> Reservation : existing reservation row (with spot_code, floor_number, qr_code_url)
    Reservation --> GW : CreateReservationResponse\n{ reservation_id, spot_id, spot_code,\n  floor_number, status, qr_code_url }
    GW --> Driver : 200 OK { reservation_id, qr_code_url }\n(replayed — no side effects)
else new request
    DB --> Reservation : not found (new request)

Reservation -> DB : Validate driver has no active reservation\n(status IN PENDING_PAYMENT, CONFIRMED)
DB --> Reservation : no active reservation

end

== User-Selected Mode (mode=USER_SELECTED) ==

alt mode = USER_SELECTED
    Reservation -> Redis : SETNX lock:spot:{spot_id} driver_id EX 30
    Redis --> Reservation : OK (lock acquired)

    Reservation -> DB : SELECT status FROM spots\nWHERE id=spot_id FOR UPDATE
    DB --> Reservation : status=AVAILABLE

else mode = SYSTEM_ASSIGNED
    Reservation -> DB : SELECT id FROM spots\nWHERE status=AVAILABLE\nAND vehicle_type=$1\nLIMIT 1 FOR UPDATE
    DB --> Reservation : spot_id (first available spot)

    Reservation -> Redis : SETNX lock:spot:{spot_id} driver_id EX 30
    Redis --> Reservation : OK (lock acquired)
end

== Common: Write Reservation & Release Lock ==

Reservation -> DB : BEGIN TRANSACTION\n  INSERT INTO reservations\n    (status=PENDING_PAYMENT, spot_id, qr_code_url, ...)\n  UPDATE spots SET status=LOCKED\n    WHERE id=spot_id\nCOMMIT
DB --> Reservation : reservation_id

Reservation -> Redis : DEL lock:spot:{spot_id}
Redis --> Reservation : OK (lock released — spot protected by DB status)

== Common: Create Payment ==

Reservation -> Payment : CreatePayment(\n  idempotency_key,\n  reference_id=reservation_id,\n  type=BOOKING_FEE,\n  amount=5000)
Payment -> DB : INSERT INTO payments\n(status=PENDING, ...)
DB --> Payment : payment_id
Payment -> PGW : Create QRIS payment (5,000 IDR)
PGW --> Payment : qr_code_url
Payment --> Reservation : { payment_id, qr_code_url }

Reservation --> GW : CreateReservationResponse\n{ reservation_id, spot_id, spot_code,\n  floor_number, status=PENDING_PAYMENT,\n  qr_code_url }
GW --> Driver : 200 OK { reservation_id, qr_code_url }

note over Driver : Driver scans QR code and pays.\nSee Seq-03 for booking payment outcome.

@enduml
